## 📚 API Documentation

The API server provides the following endpoints:

- `GET /` - Welcome message
- `GET /api/health` - Health check
- `GET /api/hello` - Hello world with optional name parameter
- `GET /api/users` - Get all users
- `POST /api/users` - Create a new user

